<style>
  .shopify-section-group-header-group,.shopify-section-group-footer-group{display:none!important}
  .ele-page{font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman",Times,serif;background:#f7f5f2;color:#1a1a1a;min-height:100vh}.ele-wrap{max-width:1040px;margin:0 auto;padding:72px 22px}.ele-kicker{color:#2D5016;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;font-weight:800;font-size:13px}.ele-page h1{font-size:clamp(42px,7vw,78px);line-height:.95;letter-spacing:-.06em;margin:14px 0 20px}.ele-page p{font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;color:#3a3a3a}.ele-regions{display:grid;gap:14px;margin-top:30px}@media(min-width:760px){.ele-regions{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}.ele-region{display:flex;min-height:220px;padding:24px;flex-direction:column;border:1px solid #dce3d5;border-radius:20px;background:#fff;text-decoration:none;transition:transform .2s ease,box-shadow .2s ease}.ele-region:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 18px 36px rgba(45,80,22,.12)}.ele-region span{color:#7b8f64;font-size:12px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase}.ele-region h2{margin:14px 0 8px;color:#2D5016;font-size:28px;line-height:1}.ele-region p{margin:0;color:#555;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}.ele-region strong{margin-top:auto;padding-top:18px;color:#2D5016;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase}.ele-faq{display:grid;gap:14px;margin-top:36px}.ele-faq details{background:white;border:1px solid #e5dfd6;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden}.ele-faq summary{cursor:pointer;padding:20px 24px;font-weight:900;font-size:19px;list-style:none}.ele-faq summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}.ele-faq div{padding:0 24px 22px}.ele-cta{display:inline-flex;margin-top:24px;padding:15px 22px;border-radius:999px;background:#2D5016;color:white!important;text-decoration:none;font-weight:900}
</style>
<main class="ele-page">
  <section class="ele-wrap">
    <span class="ele-kicker">Transfer Zones & Travel Policy</span>
    <h1>Clear pickup zones. No last-minute surprises.</h1>
    <p>We keep transfer rules transparent so guests can book with confidence before checkout.</p>
    <div class="ele-regions">
      <a class="ele-region" href="/products/living-green-chiang-mai-ethical-half-day-morning#pickup-zone"><span>Chiang Mai</span><h2>Old City pickup radius</h2><p>See the complimentary 5 km hotel transfer area and private transfer notes.</p><strong>View Chiang Mai guide →</strong></a>
      <a class="ele-region" href="/products/chonburi-ethical-half-day-morning-bangkok-departure#pickup-zone"><span>Bangkok departure</span><h2>Three pickup zones</h2><p>Review the included Bangkok districts and the Ekkamai meeting point option.</p><strong>View Bangkok guide →</strong></a>
      <a class="ele-region" href="/products/chonburi-ethical-half-day-morning-pattaya-departure#pickup-zone"><span>Pattaya departure</span><h2>City hotel transfer</h2><p>Check North, Central and South Pattaya plus the Jomtien and Nong Nooch notes.</p><strong>View Pattaya guide →</strong></a>
    </div>
    <div class="ele-faq">
      <details open><summary>Chiang Mai Transfer Zone</summary><div><p>Hotels within 5km of Chiang Mai Old City include free round-trip air-conditioned van transfers. If your hotel is outside the complimentary zone, we will confirm any small surcharge clearly before your tour date.</p></div></details>
      <details><summary>Bangkok & Pattaya Transfer (Chonburi Camp)</summary><div><p>For Chonburi camp, we include pickup from Bangkok's three core zones, including Khao San, Sathorn, Sukhumvit, Siam, Suvarnabhumi Airport and more, plus North, Central and South Pattaya. Thonburi side, Jomtien, and Nong Nooch areas may require a 100-200 THB surcharge.</p></div></details>
      <details><summary>Cancellation & Amendment Policy</summary><div><p>Free cancellation is available up to 24 hours before your tour. Full refunds are available except for basic payment-channel processing fees where applicable.</p></div></details>
    </div>
    <a class="ele-cta" href="/">Back to tours</a>
  </section>
</main>
